casebody.data:
Stark County Bar Association v. Stocker.

[Cite as Stark Cty. Bar Assn. v. Stocker (1989), 47 Ohio St. 3d 46.]

(No. 89-1559 Submitted November 8, 1989 Decided December 13, 1989.) Earl Sheehan and Frank DePasquale, for relator. Lemuel Green, for respondent. Per Curiam.

We concur with the board’s findings and recommendation. Respondent is hereby publicly reprimandéd. Costs taxed to respondent.

Judgment accordingly.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
